archimate:BusinessProcess.name: Develop Algorithmic Product Offering Pricing Matrix Definition
archimate:BusinessProcess.documentation: Brief Description Define the product offering pricing matrix and its association(s) to the specific product offering(s) to which it applies. Extended Description Develop Algorithmic Product Offering Pricing Matrix Definition defines the product offering pricing matrix based on a matrix specification and its association(s) to the specific product offering(s) to which it applies.
